2.1.2.2 Node Labels Analyzed
2.1.2.2.1 Analyzed Tree Diagram
2.1.2.2.2 Analyzed Properties
PropertyValue
Node keyAnalyzed
Technical name
Activatedtrue
Id
Description

Stage tweet is currently in in the processing pipeline. Stages are: downloaded, georeferenced, derived labels, and complete.

Downloaded - tweet is downloaded by the content hasn't been aanzlyed Georeferenced - tweet has been georeferenced, but deep learning models haven't been applied Derived labels - deep learning models were applied. Last step is to collect and process 'likes' 1 week after tweet post

Sub-Node

    "description": "Stage tweet is currently in in the processing pipeline.  Stages are: downloaded, georeferenced, derived labels, and complete.  \n\nDownloaded - tweet is downloaded by the content hasn't been aanzlyed\nGeoreferenced - tweet has been georeferenced, but deep learning models haven't been applied\nDerived labels - deep learning models were applied.  Last step is to collect and process 'likes' 1 week after tweet post"
